Reptile Zoo w/friends 💚🐍🐢🦎🐊 06.21.2025

We met some friends here after me and Jordan got back from Vegas and I’m officially obsessed! The kids loved it and wouldn’t stop talking about it on the car ride home. If you’re in Orange County you NEED to check this place out! They have alligators, snakes, turtles, lizards, chameleons, etc. Make sure to get the worms to feed the little turtles and fish at the front and the cup of veggies for the big turtles!
